<% content_for :title, 'Privacy Statement' %>
<div class="space-y-6">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">Privacy Statement</h1>

  <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-sm">
    <div class="card-body prose prose-sm max-w-none text-base-content/80">
      <p>At Flourish, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Statement outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our web app.</p>

      <h3 class="text-secondary font-bold mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h3>
      <p>When you sign up for Flourish, we collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email Address:</strong> To verify your identity, send notifications, and provide newsletters.</li>
        <li><strong>PayPal.Me Handle:</strong> To facilitate transactions as part of our app's functionality.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-secondary font-bold mt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account Management:</strong> Verifying your email address during registration and managing your account.</li>
        <li><strong>Transactions:</strong> Using your PayPal.Me handle to enable secure payments or transfers.</li>
        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Sending important updates, notifications, and newsletters about Flourish.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-secondary font-bold mt-4">3. Sharing Your Information</h3>
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties. We may share data with trusted service providers to facilitate app functionality, such as email service providers and payment processors like PayPal.</p>

      <h3 class="text-secondary font-bold mt-4">4. Data Security</h3>
      <p>We implement robust measures including encryption for data transmission and secure storage of sensitive information.</p>

      <h3 class="text-secondary font-bold mt-4">5. Your Rights</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information.</li>
        <li>Opt-out of newsletters or notifications at any time via the unsubscribe link in our emails.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-secondary font-bold mt-4">6. Cookies and Tracking</h3>
      <p>Flourish may use cookies to enhance user experience and analyze site traffic. You can control cookie settings through your browser.</p>

      <h3 class="text-secondary font-bold mt-4">7. Updates to This Policy</h3>
      <p>This Privacy Statement may be updated periodically. Significant changes will be communicated via email or the app.</p>

      <h3 class="text-secondary font-bold mt-4">8. Contact Us</h3>
      <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at: <span data-controller="support" data-support-target="email"></span></p>
      <p>Your trust is important to us, and we are dedicated to ensuring your information is used responsibly and securely.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
